Nuances & Edge Cases Handled

Bidirectional sync with loop prevention using last_updated_by

Event-driven Google Sheets sync via installable triggers

Schema consistency enforced between Sheet & DB

Duplicate row handling via primary key (id)

Partial row updates handled safely

Boolean & data type normalization

Concurrent Google Sheet edits (multiplayer-safe via last-write-wins)

Backend restart-safe (no state stored in memory)

API failure handling without corrupting data

Clear separation of concerns (routes, services, DB layer)

Secure DB access via non-root user

Scalable design (can support multiple sheets/tables)
